                <p class="team-description">
                    Mohammad Hafeez is a Qualified Mediator with the ADR Institute of Canada (Q.Med). He is a seasoned Professional with a demonstrated history of resolving conflicts among businesses, families and individuals from all walks of life.
                    Mohammad brings a wealth of knowledge and expertise on matters relating to business, workplace, family and relationship conflicts. He obtained certification in Dispute Resolution and Advanced Negotiations from York University.
                    He is a seasoned professional with 25 years of Banking, Business Management, Financial Consulting and mediation experience.
                    His expertise is handling complex business transactions and, upon call, assists other Mediators and Lawyers in such transactions.
                    Using his experience in mediation, facilitation and counselling, Mohammad Hafeez will take the time to walk you through the process and work with you towards bringing your case to agreement in a timely and efficient manner.
                    Mohammad is looking forward to helping and guiding professionals, entrepreneurs and community members through their conflicts.
                    Mediator

